===Etymology===

Gk ''[[σεισμός]]'' fr. ''[[séisme]]'' + ''-ic'' (seism(o) + ic)

===Adjective===
'''seismic'''
# Related to, or caused by an [[earthquake]] or other [[vibration]] of the [[Earth]].
# (Metaphorically) Of very large, or [[widespread]] effect.

